OL,3,CVillage pub remains shut after van
OL,4,Ccollides into front porch
OL,6,FThe middle section of the front porch
OL,7,Fthen collapsed, with pictures showing
OL,8,Froof tiles scattered over the path and
OL,9,Froad.
OL,11,FLandlady Birgit Drixelious-Benjamin
OL,12,Fsaid: "I was in the bar and suddenly
OL,13,Fthere is this massive crash, and the
OL,14,Fnext thing, glass flew into the pub
OL,15,Fand I thought it was an earthquake.
OL,17,F"I could even feel the floor moving a
OL,18,Fbit, it happened really fast, but it
OL,19,Fwas so loud I'd never heard anything
OL,20,Flike that."
