OL,3,CVillage pub remains shut after van
OL,4,Ccollides into front porch
OL,6,FPolice were immediately called to the
OL,7,Fpub at around 10.35pm and cordoned off
OL,8,Fthe area.
OL,10,FA structural engineer has been called
OL,11,Fin to assess the damage to the pub -
OL,12,Fbut the van cannot be removed until it
OL,13,Fis safe to do so.
OL,15,FA 37-year-old man from Newhaven was
OL,16,Farrested and has been charged with
OL,17,Fdrink-driving.
OL,19,FHe has been released on conditional
OL,20,Fbail to appear before Brighton
OL,21,FMagistrates' Court on 30 May.
