OL,3,CVillage pub remains shut after van
OL,4,Ccollides into front porch
OL,6,FThe bend in the road nearby is known
OL,7,Fas an accident hotspot, with calls
OL,8,Ffrom locals for the speed limit to be
OL,9,Freduced.
OL,11,FGreen Cllr Joa Saunders from Lewes
OL,12,FCouncil said: "This particular bend is
OL,13,Fa real problem because you can't see
OL,14,Fpeople crossing the road, you can't
OL,15,Fsee the cars coming in, the cars can't
OL,16,Fsee the people trying to cross.
OL,18,F"I would like to see it personally
OL,19,Fdown to 20 miles an hour and enforced
OL,20,F20 miles an hour."
