OL,4,Ccollides into front porch
OL,6,FAn East Sussex County Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The council's
OL,8,Fspeed limit policy is in line with
OL,9,Fcurrent central government guidance
OL,10,Fand current local and national
OL,11,Fevidence indicates that introducing
OL,12,F20mph speed limits on all residential
OL,13,Froads would not make best use of our
OL,14,Fresources, and that targeted
OL,15,Finterventions are more effective.
